:<font size="15">רמשׂ</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
רמשׂ / râmaś / raw-mas'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''רמשׂ'''

# Properly to [[glide]] swiftly, that is, to crawl or move with short steps; by analogy to swarm: - [[creep]], [[move]].

